_sText: AIM_TEMPLE BY UNREAL The map is designed to help aid players of whom are not effective at using eco weapons such as the MP5 or the USP, made to help players aim and control their recoil and game-style with the MP5, USP, standard kevlar (no helmet) and a single HE grenade. Special thanks to Hybrid and Matuka for their feedback on the map. www.FRAGXL.com
